{"tid":2081524,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[steam] Sea of Thieves 約戰區","createTime":"2020-06-27T09:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T09:03:27.000Z","uid":44060,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e216868103b7f83cb5d0a91fe7ca1607488f7a","tid":2081524,"uid":44060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"《Sea of Thieves》是一款重點在於與船員合作的共享世界冒險遊戲 (又稱 SWAG)，讓玩家成為自己心目中的真正海盜。想要隨著地圖解開謎題找到傳說中的寶藏嗎？要集結最勇猛剽悍的船員一起出海嗎？要到大海另一端探索未知國度嗎？我們希望能打造一款讓每個人都能實現個人冒險願望的遊戲。<br />\n讓玩家能自在體驗海盜生涯的一切。不論是結伴冒險或是單獨出航，都會在途中遇到其他船員... 但這些人究竟是敵是友呢？而您又該如何面對他們？<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\nSea of thieves 主打多人線上開放世界<br />\npve可以接商家npc運下貨物，又有尋寶任務等等。<br />\npvp鍾意簡單直接既暴力搶掠，online出海見地人架船有寶藏箱，直接開炮打爆對家架船再搶埋佢地啲箱。仲有隻game唔怕無新內容玩，因為每月都會出一次更新<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDiscord : <a href=\"https://discord.gg/nfKnmKg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FnfKnmKg&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=c11579ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/nfKnmKg</a><br />\n<br />\nSteam Link : <a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1172620/Sea_of_Thieves/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1172620%2FSea_of_Thieves%2F&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=1ce0e48f\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1172620/Sea_of_Thieves/</a><br />\n<br />\nstream version trailer <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rD974R24J-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrD974R24J-4&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=ce496159\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rD974R24J-4</a>"},{"pid":"5c10415dd30edc27e26d7451c8a968209e315762","tid":2081524,"uid":44060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:12:27.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"d441e078b1eb2faa1cc2292876949ce5ab1701aa","tid":2081524,"uid"